install ubuntu from scratch:

1. install git
sudo apt install git

2. install composer
sudo apt install curl php-cli php-mbstring git unzip php7.4-curl php-mbstring php-xml php7.4-mysql
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-and-use-composer-on-ubuntu-18-04

3. install valet
sudo apt install network-manager libnss3-tools jq xsel
composer global require cpriego/valet-linux
